:"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200110/GPBGURCBOXSN2KHROLQEQCSNMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200110%2FGPBGURCBOXSN2KHROLQEQCSNMM%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=783fd8db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200110%2FGPBGURCBOXSN2KHROLQEQCSNMM%2F&h=7b19506b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200110/GPBGURCBOXSN2KHROLQEQCSNMM/</a><br />\n<br />\n被告中大物理系學生張被指於去年11月18日在紅磡暢運道巴士站外管有汽油彈。控方指警方拘捕被告時，在他身上搜出士巴拿及汽油彈等。案件將於本月29日再訊。<br />\n法官潘兆童今批准被告的保釋申請，條件為一萬元現金、以及由中大物理系高級講師、電視節目《學是學非》的物理專家湯兆昇博士，以及新亞書院紫霞樓舍監林漢明教授各提供兩萬元人事擔保。被告並須交出旅遊證件，其間不准離港，每周三天向警方報到，每晚11時至翌晨6時宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8381e3e6a639683cfd15dc1942a08ad287a3be09","tid":2420894,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a4e2135118ab3e826d54043b5b1a0f4cf2a9f9","tid":2420894,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff859205399f2a4ba35f50c6f599a791c5cfd26","tid":2420894,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"係咪又係張卓勤條死短撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"39f2d186585c8339d341cfa17258520aa81e7af9","tid":2420894,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"一見係轉介...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b7527c59f75dc551c7f