0210224/DW3HGHPNUNC5RNCEUOIFL5HMEI/</a>"},{"pid":"e66614ba420322c0e6a413e7c3e0a719b5a1336f","tid":2420894,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"啲朋友做乜走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f413a60a0308307b040075f476e6f5ef23bae887","tid":2420894,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"辯方欲力挽狂瀾，極力爭取為被告申請擔保，惟裁判官鄭念慈以案件性質嚴重為由拒絕，男生再次還柙。<br />\n<br />\n被告於前年11月被拘捕，提堂後遭還柙，直至去年1月10日獲高院批准擔保外出。據資料顯示，當時被告獲中大物理系高級講師、經常在無綫節目《學是學非》亮相的湯兆昇博士，以及中大教授林漢明提供人事擔保，最終以現金及人事共5萬元保釋。去年6月，被告從中大物理系畢業後，獲得中大一份合約工作，其後獲裁判官免除兩人的人事擔保，並將每周向警署報到三次減為每周一次。<br />\n<br />\n不過，控方今向法庭提出撤銷被告擔保申請。<strong><span class=\"red\">據了解，辯方指被告願意恢復原本的嚴格擔保條件，而兩名教授亦願意繼續充當擔保人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然被告擔保一年間並無棄保，亦遵守向警署報到等條件，但裁判官鄭念慈認為現實情況已改變，控方加控暴動罪及修訂控罪，性質嚴重，因此撤銷擔保。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210224/DW3HGHPNUNC5RNCEUOIFL5HMEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210224%2FDW3HGHPNUNC5RNCEUOIFL5HMEI%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=90c1f77d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210224%2FDW3HGHPNUNC5RNCEUOIFL5HMEI%2F&h=d79f76bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210224/DW3HGHPNUNC5RNCEUOIFL5HMEI/</a>"},{"pid":"a750c6c1a46796233c22092468c8610199a86d83","tid":2420894,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"而家落左柯打理大係下面唔俾保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d820d9ecf60193dbe3bd3329301ef9b8c7c5ee4","tid":2420894,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb67782dc08c85a80e6d39dd84495ae89ad6963","tid":2420894,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f6918a17d2af4ecb4524478d10c11fd05b3e4946","tid":2420894,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">1534 裁判官撤銷被告保釋‼️</span></strong>"}}